  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1926670/extras/cfba71484a103761676f7f87c032da6b.poster.avif?t=1670343404\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1926670/extras/cfba71484a103761676f7f87c032da6b.webm?t=1670343404\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1926670/extras/cfba71484a103761676f7f87c032da6b.mp4?t=1670343404\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >bullet rain</h2><br>Incessant attacks will leave you trapped not knowing what to do.<br>Will his strategies be able to overcome the absolute combat power of his enemy's troops?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1926670/extras/c91b67bf40cb22dbee44f5e24be45d44.poster.avif?t=1670343404\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1926670/extras/c91b67bf40cb22dbee44f5e24be45d44.webm?t=1670343404\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1926670/extras/c91b67bf40cb22dbee44f5e24be45d44.mp4?t=1670343404\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Frantic Combat</h2><br>In this combat, keep in mind that the opponent will spare no efforts to eliminate you.<br>Make this adventure very exciting, keeping moving, to stay alive, only with strategies will you succeed.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1926670/extras/82257ef91f970c6f099f065be615c83b.poster.avif?t=1670343404\" width=500 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1926670/extras/82257ef91f970c6f099f065be615c83b.webm?t=1670343404\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1926670/extras/82257ef91f970c6f099f065be615c83b.mp4?t=1670343404\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cyber Dungeon: Excalibur</h2><br>Cyber Dungeon: Excalibur is a rogue-like game in which you'll have to deal with a large amount of enemies and a suppression of bullets from all sides, in addition to having to be careful where you're going and where you are, so you don't end up getting lost in the levels and getting trapped in a dead end.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1926670/extras/cfba71484a103761676f7f87c032da6b.poster.avif?t=1670343404\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1926670/extras/cfba71484a103761676f7f87c032da6b.webm?t=1670343404\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1926670/extras/cfba71484a103761676f7f87c032da6b.mp4?t=1670343404\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >bullet rain</h2><br>Incessant attacks will leave you trapped not knowing what to do.<br>Will his strategies be able to overcome the absolute combat power of his enemy's troops?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1926670/extras/c91b67bf40cb22dbee44f5e24be45d44.poster.avif?t=1670343404\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1926670/extras/c91b67bf40cb22dbee44f5e24be45d44.webm?t=1670343404\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1926670/extras/c91b67bf40cb22dbee44f5e24be45d44.mp4?t=1670343404\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Frantic Combat</h2><br>In this combat, keep in mind that the opponent will spare no efforts to eliminate you.<br>Make this adventure very exciting, keeping moving, to stay alive, only with strategies will you succeed.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1926670/extras/82257ef91f970c6f099f065be615c83b.poster.avif?t=1670343404\" width=500 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1926670/extras/82257ef91f970c6f099f065be615c83b.webm?t=1670343404\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1926670/extras/82257ef91f970c6f099f065be615c83b.mp4?t=1670343404\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cyber Dungeon: Excalibur</h2><br>Cyber Dungeon: Excalibur is a rogue-like game in which you'll have to deal with a large amount of enemies and a suppression of bullets from all sides, in addition to having to be careful where you're going and where you are, so you don't end up getting lost in the levels and getting trapped in a dead end.",
